+<a name="61009-0015.htm_para33"></a>
+<p><a name="stpa_361"></a><a name="06100910000603"></a>The order allows government regulations on signage to be excessive, burdensome and permanent. We have enough burdensome and permanent graffiti in Northern Ireland without having uncontrolled no-smoking signs all over the walls of our lovely buildings. There should be controls and management, and there should be liability for planning permission and proper management.</p>
 
