+<a name="61009-wms0004.htm_para42"></a>
+<p><a name="wms_stpa_322"></a><a name="0610055000407"></a>For students who are not being charged variable fees (primarily students who entered higher education before 1 September 2006), the maximum fee payable will increase from &#163;1,200 to &#163;1,225.</p>
 
-				<tr>
+<a name="61009-wms0004.htm_para43"></a>
+<p><a name="wms_stpa_323"></a><a name="0610055000408"></a>The increased fee amounts have been authorised by the Student Fees (Amounts) (England) (Amendment) Regulations 2006, which will come into force on 1 September 2007.</p>
 
