-<p><a name="wa_st_196"></a>
-<a name="0610054001171"></a><b><a name="61009w0014.htm_spmin4"></a><a name="0610054002352"></a>The Minister of State, Home Office (Baroness Scotland of Asthal):</b> No payments have been made to Philip Gould Associates by the Home Office or any of its agencies in each of the past 10 years.</p>
