-		</tr>
+<ul><a name="0610054001931"></a>
+<p><a name="wa_qnpa_283"></a>Whether, since 2000, the Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs has obtained or received a legal opinion concerning the discharge of raw sewage into the River Thames and compliance with the European Union Urban Waste Water Directive; and whether they will place a copy of any such opinion in the Library of the House.[HL7359]</p>
